PitchForge for Claude Code
Copyright 2026 Two-Weeks-Team

This product includes software developed by the Two-Weeks-Team.

Built with Claude Opus 4.7 (Anthropic).

Sibling product to Preview Forge for Claude Code
(https://github.com/Two-Weeks-Team/PreviewForgeForClaudeCode).

The reference example `plugins/pitch/examples/preview-forge-160s/deck.html`
is a verbatim copy of the v2 cinematic storyboard deck originally produced
in the Preview Forge repository's `claudedocs/winning-storyboard-deck-v2.html`
during the design conversation that produced this plugin's specification.

The hero-copy methodology in this plugin acknowledges the cadence of
"Attention Is All You Need" (Vaswani et al., 2017, NeurIPS) as a positioning
pattern. The reference is structural; no content from the paper is reproduced.
